# MONEI Payment Module Commands

## Build/Test Commands
```bash
./bin magento setup:di:compile      # Compile DI
./bin magento setup:upgrade         # Run upgrades
./bin magento cache:clean           # Clean cache
./bin test/unit <dir>               # Run unit tests for specific directory
./bin test/unit-coverage <dir>      # Generate unit test coverage
./bin test/unit-xdebug <dir>        # Run unit tests with Xdebug
./bin test/unit --testdox           # Run utit tests with arguments
```

